highlights.text: Justin Bieber has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “DAISIES” is the highest at #8.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 862 days straight.
“DAISIES” by Justin Bieber is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #8.
“Última Noite” by NATTAN and Léo Foguete is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 48 spots at #107.
